author: seattlepi.com
title: Man shot dead at Santa Clara house party
text:
SANTA CLARA, Calif. (AP) â€” Authorities say a 22-year-old man has been shot and killed during a house party in Santa Clara.
The San Jose Mercury News reports ( http://bayareane.ws/1LQIyn1 ) that officers had responded Sunday to reports of a shooting at the home.
Officers arrived to find a man, who has not yet been identified, in the backyard with gunshot wounds.
Police tried to revive the man by administering CPR, but were unsuccessful. He was pronounced dead at the scene.
___
Information from: San Jose (Calif.) Mercury News, http://www.mercurynews.com
